data.description: Welcome HOME! This beautiful home is located in North East Lehigh Acres close to the Fire Station off Joel Blvd. It is on a very quite street with very few Neighbors. The lot is approximately 1/2 Acre, with grass on most of it and the back is partially wooded. There is plenty of room to add a POOL. The Home has been well maintained and offers a lot of outdoor space in front on the patio or outback on the Screened Lanai. If you are looking to see the Stars at Night, and have a little privacy this is your home. Come Visit Today!
